data.description: The Greens at Redmond. A desirable patio home located on a quiet cul de sac adjacent to the clubhouse. Great room floor plan with natural gas fireplace and vaulted ceiling. A morning window brings light into the kitchen featuring tile counter, oak cabinets and eating bar. Enjoyable entry patio for morning sun and spacious rear yard with patio and mature landscaping for afternoon shade. Large side yard and attached double garage. A wonderful easy living opportunity.
